    "dos": [
      "Use shoes to ground the outfit, support the occasion, and reinforce the intended silhouette.",
      "Match footwear polish, contrast, and seasonal weight to the outfit and setting."
    ],
    "donts": [
      "Do not let footwear break the occasion or weather logic of the look.",
      "Do not use statement shoes with already busy outfits unless the rest of the styling is intentionally quiet."
